#. Plugin Name of the plugin
#: woo-payment-reminder.php
msgid "Woo Payment Reminder"
msgstr "Woo Payment Reminder"

#. Plugin URI of the plugin
#: woo-payment-reminder.php
msgid "https://github.com/nobodyguy/woo-payment-reminder"
msgstr "https://github.com/nobodyguy/woo-payment-reminder"

#. Description of the plugin
#: woo-payment-reminder.php
msgid ""
"Automatically sends payment reminder emails after a configurable number of "
"days."
msgstr ""
"Versendet automatisch Zahlungserinnerungs-E-Mails nach einer "
"konfigurierbaren Anzahl von Tagen."

#. Author of the plugin
#: woo-payment-reminder.php
msgid "Jan Gnip"
msgstr "Jan Gnip"

#. Author URI of the plugin
#: woo-payment-reminder.php
msgid "https://github.com/nobodyguy"
msgstr "https://github.com/nobodyguy"

#: classes/class-wc-email-payment-reminder.php:10
#: classes/class-wc-email-payment-reminder.php:12
msgid "Payment Reminder"
msgstr "Zahlungserinnerung"

#: classes/class-wc-email-payment-reminder.php:11
msgid ""
"Sends a reminder email for unpaid orders after a configurable number of days."
msgstr ""
"Sendet eine Einnerungs-E-Mail für nicht bezahlte Bestellungen nach einer "
"einstellbaren Anzahl an Tagen."

#: classes/class-wc-email-payment-reminder.php:13
msgid "Reminder: Complete your payment for order #{order_id}"
msgstr "Erinnerung: Schließe die Zahlung für Bestellung #${order_id} ab"

#: classes/class-wc-email-payment-reminder.php:30
msgid "Enable/Disable"
msgstr "Aktivieren/Deaktivieren"

#: classes/class-wc-email-payment-reminder.php:32
msgid "Enable this email"
msgstr "Diese E-Mail aktivieren"

#: classes/class-wc-email-payment-reminder.php:36
msgid "Days before first reminder"
msgstr "Tage vor der ersten Erinnerung"

#: classes/class-wc-email-payment-reminder.php:42
msgid "Days before second reminder"
msgstr "Tage vor der zweiten Erinnerung"

#: templates/emails/payment-reminder.php:9
#: templates/emails/plain/payment-reminder.php:7
#, php-format
msgid "Hello %s,"
msgstr "Halloo %s,"

#: templates/emails/payment-reminder.php:13
#, php-format
msgid ""
"We noticed that your order <strong>#%s</strong> is still awaiting payment."
msgstr ""
"Wir haben festgestellt, dass deine Bestellung <strong>#%s</strong> noch auf "
"Zahlung wartet."

#: templates/emails/payment-reminder.php:18
#: templates/emails/plain/payment-reminder.php:12
msgid ""
"To complete your purchase, please proceed with the payment at your earliest "
"convenience."
msgstr ""
"Um Ihren Kauf abzuschließen, führe bitte die Zahlung so schnell wie möglich "
"durch."

#: templates/emails/payment-reminder.php:23
msgid "Pay Now"
msgstr "Jetzt bezahlen"

#: templates/emails/payment-reminder.php:27
#: templates/emails/plain/payment-reminder.php:19
msgid "If you have already completed the payment, please ignore this message."
msgstr ""
"Wenn du die Zahlung bereits vorgenommen hast, ignoriere bitte diese "
"Nachricht."

#: templates/emails/payment-reminder.php:29
#: templates/emails/plain/payment-reminder.php:22
msgid "Thank you for shopping with us."
msgstr "Vielen Dank für deinen Einkauf bei uns."

#: templates/emails/plain/payment-reminder.php:9
#, php-format
msgid "We noticed that your order #%s is still awaiting payment."
msgstr ""
"Wir haben festgestellt, dass deine Bestellung #%s noch auf Zahlung wartet."

#: templates/emails/plain/payment-reminder.php:15
msgid "Payment link:"
msgstr "Zahlungslink:"
